<button class="accordion">How do I become a certified online health and wellness consultant?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Some online health and wellness consultant positions require a college degree, and others require a background in healthcare, diet and nutritional training. Generally, wellness consultants who work for a large company or a healthcare agency have a college degree in a health-related field like nutrition or sports medicine.</p>
