<button class="accordion">How can you improve health and wellness in the workplace?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Here are some things you can do to promote health and wellness in the workplace:</p>
<p></p><li>Focus on general prevention</li>
<p></p><li>Encourage healthier eating</li>
<p></p><li>Develop a smoke-free workplace</li>
<p></p><li>Encourage more physical exercise</li>
<p></p><li>Improve mental health</li>
<p></p><li>Avoid long chair time</li>
<p></p><li>Encourage healthy weights</li>
<p></p><li>Reduce alcohol intake.</li><p></p></div>
<button class="accordion">How do I start an online health and wellness programme?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Here are some ways to start an online health and wellness programme:</p><p></p><li>Conduct assessments</li>
<p></p><li>Obtain management support</li>
<p></p><li>Establish a wellness committee</li>
<p></p><li>Develop goals and objectives</li>
<p></p><li>Establish a budget</li>
<p></p><li>Design wellness programme components</li>
<p></p><li>Select wellness programme incentives or rewards</li>
<p></p><li>Communicate the wellness plan.</li><p></p></div>
